Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.69,0:00:46.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead
Comment: 1,0:00:47.94,0:00:48.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.57,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,开端便是一切都顺序错乱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不变的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人还知吃吃喝喝舞中作乐
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦无止境  社会压力超负荷
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早间新闻将这常态播放着
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼着我睁开双眼  漱口洗脸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.17,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一个汉堡打发  能不能来点奇迹使天地异变
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什么梦呢我傻吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.51,0:01:11.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.88,0:01:12.97,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.97,0:01:13.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.55,0:01:14.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.89,0:01:16.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.39,0:01:18.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.94,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久后人生即将画上句号
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.94,0:01:25.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,仅有空虚又怎够将我填饱？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.73,0:01:33.11,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原点  保持新鲜
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.28,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所愿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.08,0:01:46.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至尽兴  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.17,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.97,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
